    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the chicken is browning, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>,<strong> chipotle paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>tomato paste</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[275ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>chipotle stock</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse the <strong>black beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
