    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has browned, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic </strong>and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Add the <strong>chipotle stock</strong>, <strong>drained black beans </strong>and your<strong> chilli flakes </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) to the pan and bring to the boil</p><p>Once boiling, cook, covered, for a further 10-12 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the sauce has thickened</p>",
