    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> diced avocado</strong>, <strong>sliced spring onion </strong>and<strong> crumbled feta</strong> in a small bowl</p><p>Add the<strong> </strong>juice of <strong>half </strong>the<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>lime </strong>and stir it all together – this is your<strong> feta & avocado salsa</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime </strong>into wedges</p>",
